    "description": "Endpoints aligned with `src/remote/apiPaths.ts` (partner subscription plans, subscriptions, portfolios, posts) and `src/services/partnerManagementService.ts`.\n\n**Auth:** `Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}` (see `apiRequest` in `src/remote/apiHelper.ts`).\n\n**Base URL:** Collection variable `baseUrl` — default matches `AppConstant.BASE_URL` in `src/constant/AppConstant.ts` (no trailing slash; paths start with `/`).\n\n**HTTP methods:** Create/update use `POST`/`PUT` with JSON body (same object shapes the UI sends via `saveSubscriptionPlan` / `savePartnerSubscription`). Void operations use `PUT` to the void URL (no body required).\n\n**List response (frontend):** Parses `records`, `totalPages`, and `stats` from either top-level `data` or `data.data` (see service).\n\n**Mock mode:** `USE_MOCK_PARTNER_MANAGEMENT_API` in the service skips these calls until backend is wired.\n\n**Types & mock seeds:** `SubscriptionPlanModel`, `PartnerSubscriptionModel`, `PostModel` under `src/pages/partnerManagement/...`; sample rows in `src/mockData/partnerManagementMockData.ts`. Portfolio rows match `PortfolioRow` in the service file.",
